{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1916ead921","title":"林彪关于宣传工作的一封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d4840898f9","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":13,"articleId":"1916ead921"}],"tags":[{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2ca0c06676","type":"title","text":"关于宣传工作的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"118c7bf7b0","type":"authors","text":"林彪","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"1284da6015","type":"appellation","text":"军委各总部、各军兵种、各军区：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"7bf10688ff","type":"paragraph","text":"关于宣传工作问题，多年来，我曾向《解放军报》、《人民日报》负责同志多次谈过宣传内容问题，就是要在—切埸合和宣传的各种方式，都应突出对毛主席的宣传，对毛主席思想和毛上席革命路线的宣传，而不要宣传我。为此，特重新提出以下各点，盼同志们严格注意：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"cb94827189","type":"paragraph","text":"一、不要在街上和刊物中，宣传“树立林副主席的崇高威望”的口号。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"eb7567f02d","type":"paragraph","text":"二、不要出我的语录和文集。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"7118f5f3bf","type":"paragraph","text":"三、戏剧、电影、小说中，不要有叙述我的革命历史的事迹。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"9cb1049a5f","type":"paragraph","text":"四、不要呼喊“祝林副主席永远健康”的口号。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"dfad64a372","type":"paragraph","text":"五、最近各地开学习毛主席著作积极分子会，要求我题词均很多。鉴于最近一次题词引起了个别地方两派的纠粉，因此，一概不再题词了。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"cfa0cf3ce1","type":"paragraph","text":"六、应大力突出宣传毛主席和党十央，最好完全不要提到我。在万—需要提到我时，也无论如何不可超过十分之一的比例。这样，才能造成宣传的统一性和集中性。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"fc083ca229","type":"paragraph","text":"以上各点，盼在营以上干部中印发传到，务必落实。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"0ec93fdd02","type":"paragraph","text":"（部队发到营以上，地方发到县以上）","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"},{"id":"24ec08e682","type":"paragraph","text":" 林  彪一九六七年十二月十三日","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921"}],"page":{"id":"0fd8d0b114","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1916ead921","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}